trans-unit.source: NAME
trans-unit.target: NAME

trans-unit.source: dotnet -- General driver for running the command-line commands
trans-unit.target: dotnet -- General driver for running the command-line commands

trans-unit.source: SYNOPSIS
trans-unit.target: SYNOPSIS

trans-unit.source: DESCRIPTION
trans-unit.target: DESCRIPTION

trans-unit.source: is a generic driver for the Command Line Interface (CLI) toolchain.
trans-unit.target: is a generic driver for the Command Line Interface (CLI) toolchain.

trans-unit.source: Invoked on its own, it will give out brief usage instructions.
trans-unit.target: Invoked on its own, it will give out brief usage instructions.

trans-unit.source: Each specific feature is implemented as a command.
trans-unit.target: Each specific feature is implemented as a command.

trans-unit.source: In order to use the feature, the command is specified after `dotnet`, such as [`dotnet build`](dotnet-build.md).
trans-unit.target: In order to use the feature, the command is specified after `dotnet`, such as [`dotnet build`](dotnet-build.md).

trans-unit.source: All of the arguments following the command are its own arguments.
trans-unit.target: All of the arguments following the command are its own arguments.

trans-unit.source: The only time `dotnet` is used as a command on its own is to run portable apps.
trans-unit.target: The only time `dotnet` is used as a command on its own is to run portable apps.

trans-unit.source: Just specify a portable application DLL after the `dotnet` verb to execute the application.
trans-unit.target: Just specify a portable application DLL after the `dotnet` verb to execute the application.

trans-unit.source: OPTIONS
trans-unit.target: OPTIONS

trans-unit.source: Enables verbose output.
trans-unit.target: Enables verbose output.

trans-unit.source: Prints out the version of the CLI tooling.
trans-unit.target: Prints out the version of the CLI tooling.

trans-unit.source: Prints out more detailed information about the CLI tooling, such as the current operating system, commit SHA for the version, etc.
trans-unit.target: Prints out more detailed information about the CLI tooling, such as the current operating system, commit SHA for the version, etc.

trans-unit.source: Prints out a short help and a list of current commands.
trans-unit.target: Prints out a short help and a list of current commands.

trans-unit.source: The primary package cache.

trans-unit.source: Specifies whether data about the .NET Core tools usage is collected and sent to Microsoft.
trans-unit.target: Specifies whether data about the .NET Core tools usage is collected and sent to Microsoft.

trans-unit.source: **true** to opt-out of the telemetry feature (values true, 1 or yes accepted); otherwise, **false** (values false, 0 or no accepted).
